                  {
                    "cta": "Next!",
                    "text": "Hey! Today we'll learn how to close a presentation.\nA strong ending leaves a lasting impression on your audience.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/c738fcd7-439c-4138-a626-4fc2de36f5e5-Structured-Presentations---3.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Got it!",
                    "text": "First, summarize your key points.\nUse: \"To sum up, [point 1], [point 2], and [point 3].\"\n\nExample: \"To sum up, we have product-market fit, strong numbers, and we're ready to grow.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/c738fcd7-439c-4138-a626-4fc2de36f5e5-Structured-Presentations---3.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Nice!",
                    "text": "Then, thank the audience and invite questions.\nUse: \"Thank you. Happy to take questions.\"\n\nThis is simple but very professional.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/c738fcd7-439c-4138-a626-4fc2de36f5e5-Structured-Presentations---3.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Makes sense!",
                    "text": "When someone asks a question, respond clearly.\nUse: \"Good question. [Short answer].\"\n\nExample: \"Good question. We chose AWS because it was cheaper for our size.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/c738fcd7-439c-4138-a626-4fc2de36f5e5-Structured-Presentations---3.jpg",
